.TH "LIGHTNING-INVOICE-CREATE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-invoice-create \- create a BOLT-11 invoice
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning invoice-create
.I sat|any
.I label
.RI [ description ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Creates a BOLT-11 invoice via the Core Lightning daemon.
Use
.B any
as the amount for a zero-amount invoice (e.g. for donations).
If
.I description
is omitted it defaults to
.IR label .
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"bolt11":"...","payment_hash":"...","label":"...","expires_at":N}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-invoice-list (1),
.BR lightning-invoice-status (1),
.BR lightning-invoice-decode (1)
